2026-05-17T06:35:02.3317962Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-17T06:35:02.3318814Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-17T06:35:02.3319658Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-17T06:35:02.3320588Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-17T06:35:02.3321449Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
