2026-05-17T06:35:02.8829271Z 12    <!--
2026-05-17T06:35:02.8829621Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-17T06:35:02.8829941Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
