2026-05-17T06:35:02.9095044Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-17T06:35:02.9095375Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-17T06:35:02.9095704Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
